|legal (no commercial sales)<ref>{{cite news|title=Washington DC legalises marijuana possession and use|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-31634827|accessdate=February 26, 2015|work=BBC News|date=February 26, 2015}}</ref>
